cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.SE 

The paper introduces a new testing environment for learning algorithms, specifically for Bayesian ranking and selection problems, stochastic bandits, and sequential experimental design problems. These topics are typically covered in the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
